rComments: One of the best professors I've ever had, and I'm not even in the English department. Learned more useful things in this one course than I have in all my bio and physics courses combined. Excellent teacher; really flexible but had clear expectations for assignments and quizzes. Fun in-class exercises. She is a lovely person.

She really cares about her students and actually makes the class fun. As a science student, I never thought I would like English but I actually used to look forward to her class. You would literally have to TRY to get a bad mark in her class.
